{"tid":1823051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗當局據報以實彈及催淚彈驅散反政府示威者","createTime":"2020-01-13T11:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T14:13:36.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6d71c169e450e6ffe354b10e7dab0861ea01feb8","tid":1823051,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502513-20200113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502513-20200113.htm&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=7ceaa5d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502513-20200113.htm&h=2277c87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502513-20200113.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伊朗星期日繼續有民眾上街，抗議政府一度隱瞞軍方擊落烏克蘭客機，據報當局發射實彈及催淚彈驅散，人權組織要求政府，容許人民依法進行和平抗議活動。警方說，已經要求警員克制，否認有警員向示威者開槍.。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前警告德黑蘭當局，不要殺害示威者，指全世界都正注視伊朗局勢。<br />\n<br />\n墜機事件導致57名加拿大人喪生。加拿大總理杜魯多強調，需要為遇難者尋求正義，全面了解為什麼會發生這宗可怕的悲劇，承諾會向伊朗政府尋求答案，向家屬交代。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部希望事件能夠妥善處理，避免局勢進一步複雜化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVxNmXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVxNmXx.jpg&h=22e0cc59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7637d0d601429d74e0f00e9a512917a088439df5","tid":1823051,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:04:58.000Z","msg":"對工會有興趣嘅手足們，唔該幫推呢個post：<br />\n<br />\n【吳敏兒和你組工會】＊此活動必須報名<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822912</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09a7b9954fe2c2fdff3a427d312eccc990624ec7","tid":1823051,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 